"Greenscape Dagan Hunt":
"Numerous sightings and intel from recon
units indicate that D-arkers are gathering
in the Greenscape on Naberius.
ARKS operatives are to head to the Greenscape
immediately and wipe out any Dagans there.


----------------------------------------
Complete by obtaining 100 quest points.
Points are obtained by defeating Dagans."
